title: Bobby’s Ex Wrote A New Song About Him + Brothers Osborne On Their Gift To Amy’s Son + Wedding’s Makin’ People Crazy!: Angry Bride Begs for Photoshop
itunes:title: Bobby’s Ex Wrote A New Song About Him + Brothers Osborne On Their Gift To Amy’s Son + Wedding’s Makin’ People Crazy!: Angry Bride Begs for Photoshop
description:
Amy brought up that Bobby’s ex-girlfriend, Lindsay Ell has new music coming out about the last 2 years of her life. Bobby shows Amy the song title that she’s releasing. Brothers Osborne stop by as the Friday Morning Conversation to talk about their new live album and we debut a new segment about how weddings make people go crazy!
